-- Copper in London Drops as Much as 0.4% to $6,670 a Ton; Lead Climbs 0.6%
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-25T00:05:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/copper-in-london-drops-as-much-as-0-4-to-6-670-a-ton-lead-climbs-0-6-.html

          
          
             Copper in London dropped 0.4 percent
to $6,670 a metric ton today. Lead climbed 0.6 percent to $1,830
a ton.  
          
          


  


        